ower for those with the will to harness them.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>These immensely powerful relics will be available at an altar in the Divine Shrine for 7,000 Divine Gems starting <strong>tomorrow April 15th<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"724\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/arthro1-1024x724.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1281\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/arthro1-1024x724.png 1024w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/arthro1-300x212.png 300w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/arthro1-768x543.png 768w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/arthro1.png 1152w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"717\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/arthro3-1024x717.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1288\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/arthro3-1024x717.png 1024w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/arthro3-300x210.png 300w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/arthro3-768x537.png 768w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/arthro3.png 1149w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>DIVINE SHRINE UPDATE:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/image-3233-1024x318.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1284\" width=\"735\" height=\"205\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Alongside the new Arthropod Relics, we\u20